item.description:
Summer Beat! (stylized in all-caps) is the second mini album by TWS. It will be released on June 24, 2024 with "If I'm S, Can You Be My N?" serving as the album's title track.
"Hey! Hey!" was pre-released on June 5, 2024.
The physical album comes in two versions: Our and Now.

  4. "Double Take" - 2:19
